20:43.350 --> 20:44.110
Menurutmu,

20:44.310 --> 20:46.040
apakah kita datang terlambat?

20:47.480 --> 20:48.030
Tidak.

20:49.640 --> 20:50.440
Yakin begini?

20:51.350 --> 20:52.330
Situasi tadi malam

20:52.330 --> 20:53.460
